To check this high load average issue

1) check the Processes with high cpu usage using 
   "top" command

   check the process in nessasary or not, if not kill the process or restart the process.
   If still CPU usage is high then upgrade your CPU

2) Check the load on disk using
   "iostat" command

3) check for the disk utilization using 
   "df -h" command

   if disk usage is full then add the new disk this might reduce the load
